  "title": "Sales Consultant",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Highlights:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Attractive Overall Salary Package (With Basic $3,200 + Incentive + Sales Comms)</li>\n  <li>Provide systematic training (Both Theory &amp; Hands-on)</li>\n  <li>6 Days: Mon-Fri 10am -8pm (break 1 hr); Sat 10am-7pm (break 1hr); Sun &amp; PH: Off</li>\n  <li>6 Off days/ month</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Job Scope:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage daily clinic operations</li>\n  <li>Maintain high clinical quality and service standards</li>\n  <li>Work with doctors to establish policies, protocols, and procedures</li>\n  <li>Communicate with customers through various channels</li>\n  <li>Establish strong after sales relationships with customers</li>\n  <li>Provide professional skin/hair/body analysis and suggest appropriate aesthetic treatments and products</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>At least 1-2 years of experience in Aesthetics Clinic/Beauty/Sales or related industries</li>\n  <li>Candidate may be required to work on retail hours and weekend (Saturday, OFF on Sunday &amp; PH)</li>\n  <li>Well Groomed, motivated, resourceful, sales and service oriented</li>\n  <li>Team player with excellent interpersonal communication skills</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</strong></p>",
